Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 沒人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.00,0:01:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.69,0:01:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋皇子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.09,0:01:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋算是什麼稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對一國皇子用的什麼口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.82,0:01:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.36,0:01:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是恩維變身的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我把客房服務功能表全部報給你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 是本人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你 不是假貨吧 你這豆…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說誰是豆丁小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.43,0:02:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 是本人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}黑暗的門
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這裡到底是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.91,0:02:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候被庫拉多尼吞進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的肚子裡不可能這麼寬敞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我們待過的荒廢小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 這裡也有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉的車子？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.36,0:02:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些火恐怕也是大佐的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的在庫拉多尼肚子裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但確實在一個不太妙的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麟 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿爾的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有手的話 就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾沒有被吞進來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾那傢伙在擔心我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道這裡是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恰巧覺醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.26,0:03:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心靈感應能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛力克心靈感應
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 弟弟喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遍地是各種建築和白骨屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時代完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡到底有沒有出口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:03:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有的話就做一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做？在哪裡做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 給我火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有到底的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牆壁 找牆壁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 不管多寬敞的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直走就能走到頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.09,0:04:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出口也能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪裡去了 小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是被野狗吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙妳的 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅是天生有病無法長大的大熊貓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:05:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被父母丟棄後 我撿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就當成我的姐妹一樣撫養了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,張族在清國中也是幾乎沒有權力的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最下層的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許就是這個原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互都是弱者就相互吸引了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 最初可能就是同情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.83,0:05:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像家人一樣生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起經受磨難
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說 它成為了不可缺少的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:06:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有那孩子在 我才能忍耐苦難
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能穿越沙漠也是因為有那孩子在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 本來就沒有穿越的必要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必為了長生不老這種不明不白的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專程地…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不把長生不老的方法帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不獻給皇帝陛下取得信任的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的一族這麼下去會滅亡的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以和那孩子一起來到這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 別哭了 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離日出還有時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在憲兵也很少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幫我一起找嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:06:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的族人在上次內亂中滅亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對妳說的弱小一族之存亡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常在意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.42,0:07:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 不找了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 現在就去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳下是這種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也太累人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 而且一直沒有出口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.41,0:07:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓你吃個飽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃多少吃多少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想睡多少睡多少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麟？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:07:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要退出嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.32,0:07:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒出息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你連這種地方都要耍餓倒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來 走起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個沒骨氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能死在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的一個人走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要一個人走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想和你一起死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你也有等著你的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 如果還有說話的力氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:09:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少有食物的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎 麟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮製品是能吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒腳癬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這像是有嗎 傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飽了 吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.99,0:09:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小時候的修行比起來沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道這裡是哪裡比較困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 暫時人還精神就能接著找出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真樂觀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是對活下去很執著而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要稍微想放棄的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:10:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾的鐵拳和怒吼就飛過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.39,0:10:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是恩維
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我出口在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.02,0:10:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不美 愛德華·愛力克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 首先要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs60}（看錯你了）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs60}（吵死了吵死了）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 這裡沒有出口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是幹了多餘的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我恩維也被連累了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是庫拉多尼肚子裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.71,0:10:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說是肚子裡也可以說不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼之小…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍊金術師沒注意到這裡是哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來被庫拉多尼吞下去的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個感覺曾在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:10:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有印象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.81,0:10:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你過去曾經歷過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理之門
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那裡不是這樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全白的空間裡有一扇門
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真貨是那樣的地方呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真貨？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫拉多尼是父親大人製作的真理之門的失敗作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說…什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是父親大人的力量也沒能做成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理之門的失敗品
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡應該說是現實和真理的夾縫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夾縫？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有出口和出去的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是等待力量用盡 壽命完結
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.17,0:11:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都只能在這裡等待死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能有這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩維 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然沒有出口？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡死去？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經約定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人一起恢復原樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作這個什麼門的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的父親大人到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是布拉德雷大總統嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布拉德雷？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.84,0:12:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙只是個普通的人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.91,0:12:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.08,0:13:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用人命的賢者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大總統也是的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修瓦爾戰爭也是你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修瓦爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有比那更愉快的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那個內亂的契機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得是軍隊的將校誤殺了一個伊修瓦爾的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是殺死小孩的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.91,0:13:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從尤基先生那裡聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.41,0:14:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修瓦爾的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那心情可真是愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子彈一發內亂就這麼迅速擴張
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太爽快了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我變身的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反對軍事介入伊修瓦爾的穩健派的將校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連辯解機會都沒有就被軍事法庭判決了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類真是容易控制的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射殺了沒有任何罪孽的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞了我們的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把伊修瓦爾人逼上絕路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,產生出斯卡這種復仇機器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪走了溫莉雙親的真正兇手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他居然紋絲不動？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打嗎 小鬼們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德 退後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正全員都要死在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為去冥界的土特產給你們看個好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在森林裡戰鬥的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到他的腳邊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.86,0:15:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他是那個樣子 但體重可不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的本體相當的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:15:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這哪裡是人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製造出來的根本不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會被父親大人罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.58,0:16:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有父親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製造了人造人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製造了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞下去的質量到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼機關
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.84,0:17:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想 再想想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經說好要兩個人一起恢復原樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫拉多尼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.53,0:17:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶我去你父親那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是人柱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我是人柱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人柱到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前已經確認的有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛力克兄弟兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬可醫生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.99,0:17:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可沒有能打開門的神經
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 另一個人柱候補馬斯坦古君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大總統說想好好談談
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼讓我活著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓你理解自己的立場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊從什麼時候開始服從人造人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從這個國家誕生開始就埋下的伏筆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直看著我們的掙扎而竊笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休斯准將的葬禮也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你顫抖的手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是裝出來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一個軍人的死 所有人都太過喧囂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍服會成為喪服 這點事早就應該知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休斯准將的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葬禮中吵得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也應該有孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.15,0:19:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能說出那種
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.36,0:19:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說傑利姆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他知道了一直尊敬的父親是人造人會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是威脅我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白費力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不可能成為我的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會成為你的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍克愛中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.17,0:19:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才人事局的人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令我前往南方司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.78,0:19:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普雷達少尉去西方司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:20:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾蔓准尉被決定調任北方司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是霍克愛中尉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是人事局的雅各普列夫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人事局
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是大總統輔佐官休特里希
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是調職命令嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拆開了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼 這不可能的人事調任
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被貶到什麼地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任命莉莎·霍克愛中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從明日起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任職中央司令部…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.19,0:20:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大總統輔佐官
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,0:20:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:20:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅伊·馬斯坦古大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愉快 愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 完全不愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做出武器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個血海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不缺鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你趣味真差
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有 明顯很帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能打嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.01,0:21:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟那個軀體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.51,0:22:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且剛才的攻擊 肋骨斷了兩三根
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.77,0:22:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不給這傢伙點厲害的就不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫拉多尼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.78,0:22:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.64,0:22:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.84,0:22:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人在中央都市？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.43,0:24:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗躍的靈魂是通向未來的道標嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.30,0:24:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年喲 戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.47,0:24:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和真實邂逅 知道黑暗的深度
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.75,0:24:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 鋼之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.19,0:24:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.93,0:24:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第26話 再會
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.21,0:24:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說再見
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.59,0:24:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為相信還會再次相見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.86,0:00:06.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}純白的景色在向我招手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.23,0:00:12.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur4}我即將起程   前往那未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:21.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}迷茫的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:24.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在灰色的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:30.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在不斷變化的地圖裡 攙雜著各種夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:32.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:36.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}即使以我這微小的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:43.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}也能走到那雲的彼端嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:44.69,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}故作堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:46.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}卻受了傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.26,0:00:49.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}彷彿看透了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.31,0:00:50.87,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}從天上落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:53.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}點點雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:56.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}反復的漫反射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:59.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}筆直的光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:01.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}相互交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:05.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}並不知道去向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:06.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}只管
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.72,0:01:08.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}不停地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.35,0:01:14.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}淡淡的殘影烙印在兩眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:16.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}在這片天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.06,0:01:19.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}無論身在何處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.32,0:01:22.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}一定可以到達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:27.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur4}那未曾見過的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.56,0:22:33.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fsp-1.5\fnRoman\fs35\b1}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.28,0:22:37.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}不必故作堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.61,0:22:44.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人這樣描繪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.16,0:22:49.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在牆上塗鴉的花也會搖動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:55.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人知道真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:57.84,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在漫長的路途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.84,0:23:01.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去與獲取
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.26,0:23:08.95,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}突然寂寞  也有哭泣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:16.44,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼淚也好  痛苦也好  都將化為恆星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.44,0:23:22.44,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點燃照亮明天的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.44,0:23:27.57,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉起小手  兩個人一起創造
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.57,0:23:32.79,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去搜尋星塵與光芒四射的永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.79,0:23:38.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 那天也許還會降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:44.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}即使季節依然在不斷地交替
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.43,0:23:48.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有點迷茫  也要向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.18,0:23:52.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你一起前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:56.52,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}請讓我維持到永遠


